				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Here's my little guide on how to get to level 30 with your troll:<BR>
<BR>
1. Levels 1-5: Fight in Innothule.<BR>
<BR>
2. Levels 5-10: Get a SOW and run to Nektulos forest and get a bind in Neriak. Get in a group and kill Young Kodiaks and Orcs in East Commons.<BR>
<BR>
3. Levels 10-15: Go to Lavastorm Mountains and kill Fire drakes, Rock dervishes, and Fire Sprites. Make sure you're in a good group.<BR>
<BR>
4. Levels 15-20: Go to Highpass Hold and get in a Orc group untill you build good faction with Highpass guards and citizens. Once you get the good faction, go kill gnolls because they carry Troll-sized ringmail armor.<BR>
<BR>
5. Levels 20-30: Go into Highkeep and get in Pickclaw goblin groups. Lots of good loot to sell so you can save money for better armor and weapons.<BR>
<BR>
Then? I plan on going back to Innothule and fighting in the Guk 8)<BR>
<BR>
Gracefulness Personified<BR>
30 warrior<BR>
The Rathe
