			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				    I just started a Troll Warrior the other day and they are very good. They have high strength, they regenerate fast, they have infravision, and they also start in a good newbie zone area. Another good thing that I found out was that they lvl up very fast. I got to level five in just a few hours of killing Lesser Kobolds and Frogloc's. Trolls also get their faction up with Humans quickly. I was at Freeport and I was killing orcs, after about an hour of helping humans I went into town to sell stuff and only one guard didn't like me. So Trolls are a good race if you are starting the game. 
				</font>
