				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				ok this is it. for all you peoepl thinking of being ogre or troll you should be a troll. yes ogres get the base of 140 str and 127 sta (in the case of an sk) and their intelligance is higher than trolls but even tho trolls str is 118 and their sta is only 116 it is still very high compared to other clases. ogres agility and dex are both 70. so as an ogre you may have more hp but you willg et hit alot more cause your agil is only 70 compared to trolls 83. also you may have all this str but whats the use of it when you can't hit your target because you only have 70 dex.  then there is the case of regen. from lvl 1-19 non-troll/iksar's regen hp at the rate of 1hp a tick when standing and 2hp a tick when sitting. so in a minute of sitting down they only heal 20hps!  but a troll regains hp's twice as fast.  they gain 2hp a tick(about every 6 seconds) when standing and 4hps a tick when sitting. this means that in 1 minute they gain 2 times as many hps as any other clases.  this helps alot at lower lvls were in a fight when you get hit you regain the hps quicker than they can hit you. at lvl 20-49 it doubles for everyone and normal classes are regening at the rate that a troll was at lvl 1. but a troll regens at 4hp when standing and 8 when sitting. hope this helps! so go out there and barsh dem goodz har har!
